rComments: Rubins is great. His assignments are fair, and the structure of the class is very laid-back and amazingly fun. He's easy to talk to and fun to be around in general. I loved this class!!

Funny, nice guy.  If you come to class, you'll probably get an A.  If you're looking for serious creative writing instruction, he's good for intro, but not that great at delving deeper.  Still good in office hours.
